*basics*
*tar* *gzip* *tar.gz* *extract* *zip* *archive*
tar -xf archive.tar.gz
*-x* *--extract*    extract file
*-f*                file to use
unzip <file.zip>
unrar <file.rar>

export PATH=$PATH:/home/folder/        append to *path*

chmod +x file                          Adds execute permission to file *chmod*

*install* .tar.gz package
extract package then place in /opt finnaly create a symbolic link to the executable in /usr/local/bin which is the standard for user installed apps make sure that it is on PATH and that the executable has execute permissions
